OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWelsh speakers use TikTok  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto teach the language      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Welsh speakers are turning to TikTok to
OL,6, promote the language and teach it to   
OL,7, others.                                
OL,9,FThe social media platform is helping to
OL,10,Fconnect lovers of the language with new
OL,11,Flearners.                              
OL,13,F"I think the one thing with TikTok     
OL,14,Fthat's different is the videos are     
OL,15,Fshort and sweet. You're able to engage 
OL,16,Fwith people," said one creator.        
OL,18,FIt comes as recent census data shows   
OL,19,Fthat there is a decline in Welsh       
OL,20,Fspeakers.                              
